<plot>This film explores a few days in the life of film students Jim and Laura and their nihilistic and restless group of friends. Deciding to adapt Macbeth and shoot it with a mostly homeless cast, Jim and his friends search for locations in abandoned buildings in Philadelphia. Here, their own story takes a very unexpected and cinematic turn.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?277017</url></doc>
